'''南方馬拉卡南宮'''（[[英文|英文]]：<span>Malacañang of the South，</span> [[他加祿語|他加祿文]]：Malacañang sa Habagatan）又稱'''達沃總統禮賓府'''（'''Presidential Guest House in Davao）'''或'''帕纳坎南'''（'''Panacañang）''', 是菲律賓政府位於[[達沃市|達沃市]]帕纳坎區的禮賓府。是[[菲律賓總統|菲律賓總統]]於[[棉兰老岛|棉蘭老島]]的官邸。

== 歷史 ==
南方馬拉卡南宮是由總統[[格洛丽亚·马卡帕加尔-阿罗约|格洛麗亞·馬卡帕加爾-阿羅約]]設立。於2005年，總統辦公室購入國家公務及公路局於達沃市的一個物業，並且興建一棟兩層的禮賓府。禮賓府於2007年落成<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2016/05/27/what-will-happen-to-the-malacanang-of-the-south/|title=What will happen to the ‘Malacañang of the South’?|accessdate=21 June 2016|date=27 May 2016|publisher=|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630201040/http://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2016/05/27/what-will-happen-to-the-malacanang-of-the-south/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

南方馬拉卡南宮的原意是讓菲國總統在訪問達沃和周邊地區時有一個地方居住，但是，阿羅約只在南方馬拉卡南宮住過一次，而[[貝尼格諾·阿基諾三世|貝尼格諾·阿基諾三世]]則把南方馬拉卡南宮當作訪問時的集合地方。

現任總統[[罗德里戈·杜特地|羅德里戈·杜特地]]已說過會定期使用南方馬拉卡南宮，並在那裡開內閣會議。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/06/01/duterte-bares-more-cabinet-members-476884|title=Duterte bares more Cabinet members|accessdate=21 June 2016|date=31 May 2016|publisher=|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811220329/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/06/01/duterte-bares-more-cabinet-members-476884|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 设施 ==
南方馬拉卡南宮有八間有調溫功能的房間，以便接待總統，總統下屬和貴賓。除此之外，南方馬拉卡南宮亦有會議室和總統的辦公地方。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/788367/duterte-to-hold-first-cabinet-meet-at-malacanang-of-the-south|title=Duterte to hold first Cabinet meet at ‘Malacañang of the South’|accessdate=21 June 2016|last=Cayabyab|first=Marc Jayson|publisher=|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003193916/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/788367/duterte-to-hold-first-cabinet-meet-at-malacanang-of-the-south|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2016/05/31/president-elect-duterte-cabinet-presentation-davao.html|title=President-elect Duterte to present Cabinet|accessdate=21 June 2016|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090243/https://cnnphilippines.com/news/2016/05/31/president-elect-duterte-cabinet-presentation-davao.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

南方馬拉卡南宮亦有給予國營電視台運作的地方<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestandard.com.ph/news-flash/207682/only-ptv-4-is-allowed-inside-the-presidential-guest-house-in-panacan-davao-city-.html|title=Only PTV-4 is allowed inside the Presidential Guest House in Panacan, Davao City.|accessdate=21 June 2016|publisher=|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811110324/http://www.thestandard.com.ph/news-flash/207682/only-ptv-4-is-allowed-inside-the-presidential-guest-house-in-panacan-davao-city-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

